    <text>
        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p><bibl><ptr target="#SECir"/>, <citedRange>135</citedRange> (photo)</bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>098660</citedRange></bibl>.</p>       
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                    <ab>
                        <lb n="1"/><persName type="attested" key="http://clas-lgpn2.classics.ox.ac.uk/cgi-bin/lgpn_search.cgi?id=V1-63269"><name nymRef="#Ἀρχεμονίδας">Ἀρχενομίδα<supplied reason="lost">ς</supplied></name>
                        <lb n="2"/><persName type="attested" key=""><name type="patronymic" nymRef="#Πολιάνθης">Π<unclear>ο</unclear>λιά<supplied reason="lost">ν</supplied><unclear>θ</unclear>ευς</name></persName></persName>
                        <lb n="3"/><w lemma="δεκάτα">δ<supplied reason="lost">ε</supplied>κά<supplied reason="lost">τα</supplied>ν</w>.
                    </ab>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                 <p>
                     <app loc="2">
                         <lem>Π<unclear>ο</unclear>λιά<supplied reason="lost">ν</supplied><unclear>θ</unclear>ευς</lem>
                         <rdg resp="#SECir">Πρα<supplied reason="lost">τ</supplied>α<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/><unclear>γ</unclear>ευς</rdg>
                    </app>
                     <app loc="3">
                         <lem>δ<supplied reason="lost">ε</supplied>κά<supplied reason="lost">τα</supplied>ν</lem>
                         <rdg resp="#SECir">δεκάτ<supplied reason="lost">α</supplied>ν</rdg>
                     </app>
                 </p>
               </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="fr">
                <p>Arkhénomidas fils de Polianthès <supplied reason="subaudible">a consacré ce monument</supplied> au titre de la dîme.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="en">
            <p>Archenomidas son of Polianthes <supplied reason="subaudible">dedicated this monument</supplied> as a tithe.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="it">
            <p>Archenomidas figlio di Polianthes <supplied reason="subaudible">ha dedicato questo monumento</supplied> come decima.</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>The stone is known only from a photograph, which allows to give a date from the lettering and to improve the reading of the father's name.</p>
                <p/>
            </div></body>
